Rosemary is a plant grown with the Farming skill. Level 11 farmers may plant rosemary seeds in Flower patches. A seed dibber is needed to plant the seed.

After 5 minutes or less, the planted seed will become Rosemary. The flower patch must be raked clean of weeds. Compost or Super Compost may be added prior to planting.

Rosemary take 20 minutes to mature. After being fully grown, they protect cabbages from disease.

Planting Rosemary seeds gives 12 farming experience. No xp is given for checking on the plant. If the plant is not watched, it may become diseased, then disease on the patch may be removed using plant cure. However, if left alone, the diseased patch will die. A nearby gardener will not watch over your growing rosemary.

Each plant, when picked, gives 66.5 farming experience. The plants do not grow back after they are picked. The flower may be picked after the plant is completely grown.

'''Rosemary''' is a plant grown with the [[Farming]] skill. Level 11 farmers may plant [[rosemary seed]]s in [[Flower patches]]. A [[seed dibber]] is needed to plant the seed.

After 5 minutes or less, the planted seed will become [[Rosemary]]. The flower patch must be raked clean of weeds. Compost or Super Compost may be added prior to planting.

Rosemary take 20 minutes to mature. After being fully grown, they protect [[cabbages]] from disease.

Planting Rosemary seeds gives 12 farming experience. No xp is given for checking on the plant. If the plant is not watched, it may become diseased, then disease on the patch may be removed using [[plant cure]]. However, if left alone, the diseased patch will die. A nearby gardener will not watch over your growing rosemary.

Each plant, when picked, gives 66.5 farming experience. The plants do not grow back after they are picked. The flower may be picked after the plant is completely grown.
